2026-05-14T00:07:42.9799025Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-14T00:07:42.9799843Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-14T00:07:42.9800470Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-14T00:07:42.9801054Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
