2026-05-14T00:07:43.4568511Z 21    <!--
2026-05-14T00:07:43.4568908Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-14T00:07:43.4569364Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-14T00:07:43.4569787Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-14T00:07:43.4570372Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-14T00:07:43.4570914Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-14T00:07:43.4571430Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-14T00:07:43.4571955Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-14T00:07:43.4572460Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-14T00:07:43.4572986Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-14T00:07:43.4573516Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-14T00:07:43.4573930Z 32    -->
2026-05-14T00:07:43.4574563Z 33    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
