2026-05-14T00:07:43.5207470Z 245            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-14T00:07:43.5208087Z 246            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-14T00:07:43.5208627Z 247            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-14T00:07:43.5209194Z 248            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
